OL,3,CNottingham killings 'wholly
OL,4,Cavoidable', say victims' families
OL,5,Cafter review
OL,7,FCalocane killed university students
OL,8,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,9,FKumar, both 19, as they returned from
OL,10,Fa night out in the early hours of June
OL,11,F13 last year, before killing 65-year-
OL,12,Fold school caretaker Ian Coates.
OL,14,FSpeaking of the review into Calocane's
OL,15,Fcare, Mr Coates' son James said: "If
OL,16,Fthey'd just done the job a little bit
OL,17,Fbetter or properly, maybe Valdo's
OL,18,Ftrajectory, might have been put in a
OL,19,Fdifferent direction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
