OL,7,F"Or maybe he might have been inside
OL,8,Fand getting the help he needed before."
OL,10,FCalocane was diagnosed with
OL,11,Fschizophrenia three years before
OL,12,Flaunching his van and knife attack in
OL,13,FNottingham city centre, and had been
OL,14,Fsectioned four times.
OL,16,FOne of the failures listed by
OL,17,FTuesday's report highlights that risk
OL,18,Fassessments didn't make the danger he
OL,19,Fposed clear enough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
