OL,7,FThe CQC report also questioned how
OL,8,Fwell the trust engaged with Calocane's
OL,9,Ffamily - as it found information from
OL,10,Fthem was not consistently acted upon.
OL,12,FThe parents of Grace O'Malley Kumar,
OL,13,Falso killed in the attack, believe
OL,14,Ftragedy could have been averted if
OL,15,FCalocane's care was properly delivered.
OL,17,F"Each time he was sectioned, his
OL,18,Ftreatment didn't change or people can
OL,19,Fbe bothered to change his treatment,"
OL,20,Fsaid Grace's father, Dr Sanjoy Kumar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
