OL,7,F"I'm more than convinced that this was
OL,8,Fwholly avoidable, if this person had
OL,9,Fbeen treated with any form of
OL,10,Fresponsibility whatsoever."
OL,12,FGrace's mother, Dr Sinead O'Malley,
OL,13,Fwants those in charge of his care to
OL,14,Fbe held fully responsible.
