OL,7,FShe said: "We want accountability,
OL,8,Fbecause any doctor who fails or is
OL,9,Fnegligent needs to be held accountable
OL,10,Fquite frankly, and we see that there's
OL,11,Fbeen multiple failures in the delivery
OL,12,Fof standard treatment."
OL,14,FThe CQC said Calocane had "little
OL,15,Funderstanding or acceptance of his
OL,16,Fcondition" which could "have
OL,17,Fsignificantly impaired his ability" to
OL,18,Fweigh up the pros and cons of
OL,19,Fantipsychotic treatment and the risks
OL,20,Fof discontinuing it.
