OL,7,FIt would have been possible to treat
OL,8,Fhim under section three of the Mental
OL,9,FHealth Act (MHA) 1983 ` which would
OL,10,Fhave given doctors the power to
OL,11,Fadminister drugs against his will ` on
OL,12,Fhis fourth admission to hospital in
OL,13,FJanuary 2022, the regulator said.
OL,15,FInstead, he was treated under section
OL,16,Ftwo of the act, which is usually for
OL,17,Fpatients who are not known to mental
OL,18,Fhealth services.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
